# Program
For students who want to acquire furthermore competences in Innovation and Entrepreneurship, it will be required that they participate at the *[BD (Business Development) Labs](http://www.telecom-valley.fr/blogpost/ouverture-des-inscriptions-pour-participer-à-la-10ème-édition-du-cjp-0)* . In BD labs, students are working in group (mixed with students of Business schools) and should prepare a business plan for creating an enterprise.

Note that some optional modules might not open or might be given in French only. Optional modules will be opened if more than 8 students have registered.

